  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1446980/extras/6324ea09a1247ececc4d4d39175c4f2c.avif?t=1667121959\" width=610 height=210 /></span><br><br>Quick Square is not just a square, it is a completely new form of life in a vibrant world full of danger and adventure!<br> <br>In the game, you have to move very carefully across square platforms and collect coins.<br><br>Game features:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Difficult levels<br></li><li>Convenient management<br></li><li>Bright character<br></li><li>Collecting valuable coins<br></li><li>Teleports<br></li><li>Horizontal and vertical movement along the level.</li></ul>",
